go in player.java
search tele a couple times til you see this

// initial x and y coordinates of the player
heightLevel = 0;
// the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper
// initialization packet
teleportToX = xxxx;// xxxx;
teleportToY = xxxx;// xxxx;

change the coords to your likings
